She passed Quickstrike and entered the cave.  She turned back around 
and looked at Quickstrike. "Uh, boss, where are the CR chambers, I 
could use one right now."
With mech fluid dripping from her wounds and blood all over her face 
and chest, her paws and back.  She still had a smile on her wolf face.
